# Home-Tidy Command-based Cache Cleanup
# Some tools are safer to clean with dedicated commands rather than folder deletion
# Format: command|description|target_path (optional)

[Python]
uv cache clean|Cleanup Python uv/uvx cache|~/.cache/uv

[Node.js / npm]
npm cache clean --force|Cleanup npm cache|~/.npm
yarn cache clean|Cleanup Yarn cache|~/Library/Caches/Yarn
pnpm store prune|Prune unused pnpm store items|~/Library/pnpm/store

[Docker]
docker builder prune -f|Prune Docker build cache
